        History
        -------
        
        0.0.3 (2019-03-26)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * code refactoring
        * new methods
        * query_by_service_id to fetch data by geonames, gnd and wikidata ID/URL
        
        0.0.2 (2019-03-11)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * `fetch_geonames_rdf` and `query_by_geonames_id` methods added
        
        0.0.1 (2019-03-11)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * First version
        
